    "The tutor bot effectively conveyed new knowledge to the students, although there is room for improvement in supervising and detecting relevant dialogue content.",
    "The students' ability to produce improved summaries serves as evidence of their engagement and critical thinking skills.",
    "While the tutor bot rarely delivered inappropriate responses, continuous efforts are needed to maintain its accuracy.",
    "These findings highlight the importance of ongoing refinement and enhancement of PL environments to optimize student learning outcomes.",
    "Analysis of the students' adherence to the prompt scripts showed that following structured guidelines significantly increased students' focus on intended learning objectives."
